{"tid":1628830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（和勇不分）唔同時機試下唔同既野","createTime":"2019-10-06T04:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T05:49:07.000Z","uid":196991,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c46d9b2efa0865a90e82a7881c38d803eaca45cb","tid":1628830,"uid":196991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:50:26.000Z","msg":"呢排好多風吹，搞到連登好似好分裂咁。<br />\n<br />\n我明白臨時法對大家有好大既衝擊，作為一個和理非，我都永遠堅持不割席（收皮嘢林奠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）。但係出邊好多post都有講，呢個無大台既運動，係我地成個公民社會既集體智慧而發光發亮，當中係有好多自我修正既過程，但係要有呢啲過程，我地係需要<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大量既聆聽同思考</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n我都好明白每一個人係呢場運動睇既野同做既野唔到，令到我地既想法都開始唔同。咁既話，<span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔係更加需要團結咩？</span>三毛係度帶風向，用我地既思考去擊破佢地(<span style=\"color: green;\">善用不推文去阻止佢哋入熱門</span>）。<br />\n<br />\n出面話和平遊行無用，和理非會被圍捕。但係琴日我見到和理非去銅鑼灣行，我好感動，因為佢哋話俾我地知佢哋永遠都唔割。我哋今日出去行，都係同一個目的，話俾全世界聽勇武既行為係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>對抗極權而有民意既支持</strong></span>。點解唔試下呢？<br />\n<br />\n勇武肯為和理非擋子彈，為香港可能坐十年。我地和理非都肯為勇武坐48個鐘臭格，呢個係我地既升級。<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣，尖沙咀今日不見不散<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabd37f4f14613596e0d6c0de8ed93ef28acbaec","tid":1628830,"uid":196991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beaeebd464af498e385c2238e73edf1e65709a73","tid":1628830,"uid":196991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc38757fd5699385e16dcb471d0b7e65d099b676","tid":1628830,"uid":196991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:53:37.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"a02f25b2709ed5372ad6c426fea292c7744b25b3","tid":1628830,"uid":196991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:53:47.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"d0eaf95d2887286f8131836e4ff736094ccd8503","tid":1628830,"uid":196991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:53:58.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"a523de929959cedbc92e9d24cee6cfe689c2eeb9","tid":1628830,"uid":196991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:54:09.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"71ff74f8e7befb839eb153c943c24b2931e3d555","tid":1628830,"uid":196991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:55:21.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"c1ae727764527640450597e25d029f84dd57e34f","tid":1628830,"uid":196991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:55:37.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"5422b57aa51afe6ae01d71f521e175e7e29f85a8","tid":1628830,"uid":196991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:56:14.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"e1b089f5be826702d10c4908a1c35ad71de5bda6","tid":1628830,"uid":196991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:56:24.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"66500d2288b7f0c08ef12d0c13a12b0cfa3ee79d","tid":1628830,"uid":196991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:58:50.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"9e5c9f61f694de367b719b07785c61f6370ead35","tid":1628830,"uid":196991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:59:01.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"9abbc9f79925646f11523f7bf1751ed9c540a27a","tid":1628830,"uid":249608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:01:26.000Z","msg":"幫你推<br />\n三毛收皮啦，我地絕不分化"},{"pid":"74fcc4c470eed3b38ca4735967e923df9955f484","tid":1628830,"uid":196991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:05:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c47050ce1409956d337a7fefaf9a706a37aa4bb","tid":1628830,"uid":196991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":